OL,3,C'It feels like I'm disappearing' -
OL,4,CBristol man shares reality of dementia
OL,6,FChris Richmond told ITV News West
OL,7,FCountry that living with dementia has
OL,8,Fmade him feel out of control of his
OL,9,Fown life.
OL,11,FA man from Bristol has shared his
OL,12,Fexperience of living with dementia,
OL,13,Fsaying that "it feels like he's
OL,14,Fdisappearing".
OL,16,FChris Richmond, 71, was diagnosed with
OL,17,Ffrontotemporal dementia in 2017 and
OL,18,Fnow receives full-time care.
