OL,3,C'It feels like I'm disappearing' -
OL,4,CBristol man shares reality of dementia
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News West Country, Mr
OL,7,FRichmond said the condition has made
OL,8,Fhim feel like he's losing control of
OL,9,Fhis own life.
OL,11,FHe said: "It's absolutely awful
OL,12,Fbecause I'm so used to being in
OL,13,Fcontrol, knowing what's going on, and
OL,14,Fnow I don't know what's going on half
OL,15,Fthe time.
OL,17,F"That to me is rather frightening.
OL,18,FIt's disturbing. It's sort of like,
OL,19,Fwell I don't know where the future is
OL,20,Ftaking me."
