OL,3,C'It feels like I'm disappearing' -
OL,4,CBristol man shares reality of dementia
OL,6,FAccording to Alzheimer's Research UK,
OL,7,Faround one in two people will be
OL,8,Faffected by dementia, either by having
OL,9,Fit or looking after a loved one.
OL,11,F, with nearly one million people
OL,12,Facross the country currently living
OL,13,Fwith the condition.
OL,15,FMr Richmond's wife, Angela, was a
OL,16,Fprofessional carer and now looks after
OL,17,Fher husband full-time.
