OL,3,C'It feels like I'm disappearing' -
OL,4,CBristol man shares reality of dementia
OL,6,FShe told ITV News West Country that as
OL,7,Fhis condition has progressed,
OL,8,Fcommunicating with him has become
OL,9,Fincreasingly difficult.
OL,11,F"It was like I was talking through a
OL,12,Fgauze. He didn't get what I was
OL,13,Fsaying. He was genuinely confused as
OL,14,Fto what I was actually saying," Mrs
OL,15,FRichmond explained.
OL,17,F"His memory is still there so he still
OL,18,Fknows all those types of things, but
OL,19,Fsometimes he struggles."
