OL,3,C'It feels like I'm disappearing' -
OL,4,CBristol man shares reality of dementia
OL,6,FMrs Richmond said the worst thing
OL,7,Fabout the condition is the "not
OL,8,Fknowing".
OL,10,FShe said: "He's only 71 now, so
OL,11,Freally, if we've got to go on 20
OL,12,Fyears, it's only gonna... We just
OL,13,Fdon't know. I think that's the worst
OL,14,Fthing with dementia, you just don't
OL,15,Fknow."
OL,17,FProfessor Liz Coulthard, associate
OL,18,Fprofessor in dementia neurology
OL,19,FUniversity of Bristol, said there is
OL,20,Fcurrently no cure for the condition,
OL,21,Fbut there is reason for hope.
