OL,6,F"There are a couple of drugs that have
OL,7,Fbeen positive in clinical trials and
OL,8,Fthat's exciting," she explained.
OL,10,F"But they only slow down the condition
OL,11,Fby about 20% to 30% over eighteen
OL,12,Fmonths."
OL,14,FProfessor Liz Coulthard, associate
OL,15,Fprofessor in dementia neurology at the
OL,16,FUniversity of Bristol told ITV News
OL,17,FWest Country there are ways to prevent
OL,18,Fthe condition
