OL,6,FShe added: "We need to focus on
OL,7,Fresearch so we can find the right sort
OL,8,Fof treatments that are going to help
OL,9,Fpeople and research into how we care
OL,10,Ffor people.
OL,12,F"We might not be able to stop the
OL,13,Fdisease, but we might be able to help
OL,14,Fpeople have a better quality of life."
